'''Cestian''' was the term given to the inhabitants of [[Ord Cestus/Legends|Ord Cestus]]. Originally, it referred exclusively to the native [[X'Ting]], but over time as the immigrant population boomed and the native population declined, it became used to refer to all of the [[Planet/Legends|world's]] denizens.

